data.description: Nestled in the oak trees this new build has the aesthetics and privacy that is the perfect place to call home. The large lot has established trees in front and back yard creating great shade to keep cool in the summer months.   Open floor plan with a well appointed kitchen over looking the high living area to creating cozy interior perfect for unwinding by the fireplace. The kitchen is perfect for entertaining with a large butler's pantry featuring custom cabinets and quartz countertops.  The oversized utility room is one for envy with a desk area  and island making chores a breeze.  This home boasts spacious rooms all featuring oversized walk-in closets and an upstairs bonus room can be used as a bedroom, guest suite or game room with private full bath access.
